{"tid":938732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬧市下體現形】同林峯翻撻無望 千語BB暴瘦變紙板人","createTime":"2018-12-12T14:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T15:37:10.000Z","uid":80516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"892060d9504bedae7644737269ac31dd48ace3bc","tid":938732,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"有34D 魔鬼身材嘅張馨月著得咁鬼密實，睇下千語BB就大方得多！22 吋小蠻腰任睇，再加埋呢條貼身legging ，下身若隱若現咁，BB究竟受咗咩刺激呀？<br />\n<br />\n啱啱過咗廿五歲生日，BB 突然好感性咁打咗篇千字文：「就好像我喜歡你的時候你不喜歡我，你喜歡我的時候我身邊已經有別人了」、「我錯過你了，你也錯過了最好的我了。」言語間BB似對林峯餘情未了！不過想翻撻冇咁易！對於BB嘅千字文，林峯完全不為所動，轉個頭就已經孖住新歡去東京happy!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zrrRjFm3y4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzrrRjFm3y4Y&d=D%2BlS2%2BkA0YQiF9CPsTU8cDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a18f0de5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zrrRjFm3y4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20181212/2_642943_0/-%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E7%8F%BE%E5%BD%A2-%E5%90%8C%E6%9E%97%E5%B3%AF%E7%BF%BB%E6%92%BB%E7%84%A1%E6%9C%9B-%E5%8D%83%E8%AA%9EBB%E6%9A%B4%E7%98%A6%E8%AE%8A%E7%B4%99%E6%9D%BF%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F2_642943_0%2F-%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25BD%25A2-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2592%25BB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%259C%259B-%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%25AA%259EBB%25E6%259A%25B4%25E7%2598%25A6%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%25B4%2599%25E6%259D%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=D%2BlS2%2BkA0YQiF9CPsTU8cDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=57d9c2a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F2_642943_0%2F-%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25BD%25A2-%25E5